HEADWORD: Thio-
<hw>Thi"o-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[Gr. <?/ brimstone, sulphur.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A combining form (also used adjectively)
denoting <xex>the presence of sulphur</xex>. See
<er>Sulpho-</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
